{"tid":494143,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"D毒男連剪個頭髮都煩過","createTime":"2017-12-09T10:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T10:20:50.000Z","uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"04561b90c313d8c84d07368268512e26d6f7b070","tid":494143,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T10:06:49.000Z","msg":"姐姐：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒男：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一瞓底洗頭<br />\n姐姐：佢有冇相熟師傅呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒男：（機關槍mode）無呀，我D頭髮長咗，淨係剪兩邊姐<br />\n<br />\n之後大家靜咗<br />\n毒男：你哋呢間開咗好耐喇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n姐姐：係呀，廿幾年啦<br />\n<br />\n隔咗一陣，戲肉嚟喇<br />\n毒男：&hellip;&hellip;，$/&times;&times;=眼<br />\n姐姐：沖到水入眼？即叫佢瞓上D幫佢抹<br />\n毒男：唔係呀！幫我沖下對眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住兩個姐姐討論點沖<br />\n我洗完頭一起身見到姐姐用仔毛巾包住花灑頭，<br />\nD水好似洗面咁沖落毒男塊面<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒男個樣梳乾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後我同洗頭姐姐兩個打晒眼色係到笑毒男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6507578e23af8fb3d9731a912fb17501bc8e4a","tid":494143,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T10:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hk01.com/media/images/339062/xlarge/5633bf89eb4a5ab5b070eeeda8fbbb6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F339062%2Fxlarge%2F5633bf89eb4a5ab5b070eeeda8fbbb6b.jpg&h=a0c02e7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29b1c7af7b1150eb8ad26a0879e80a50cf4a59c9","tid":494143,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T10:07:40.000Z","msg":"<